{
  "stem": "24515.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother was too young, but anybody my age, 16 and old, I've forgotten which-- 17, whatever-- we went before tribunals, which were going to judge our loyalty, our-- you know, how far we could be trusted.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we could get three classifications, either you couldn't very well be trusted, and then you got put in an internment camp immediately.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or you could, but very restricted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or you are really trustworthy, and you can go where you'd like and do what you like.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I got number one, the top one, the best one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wanted to give me number two, but I explained to them why I wanted number one, so they gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after the Fall of France, [INAUDIBLE]--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Fall of France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Obviously there was a fair amount of panic and pressure in England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we know now that some idiot must have given the-- the order, intern the lot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't intern the lot-- they didn't have enough room for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in that first thing, I got caught.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was interned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I packed a [INAUDIBLE] bag ready for this, against this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were interned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my internment was in a way rather funny.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was what the newspapers later wrote it up as a temple of horror, and of-- of nastiness.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The German-- I mean-- the British concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was nothing of the sort.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- didn't like it, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they tried terribly hard to release the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was trouble with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] for having been taking in, your livelihood, that you had, maybe, built up in a year or two, of course, was gone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they did say that anyone under 18 should be released.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was released.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
